Booster vmf.

I copied a booster out my WIP and posted it here.
To change the strength see the outputs, requires no filters.

The gravity keyvalue with the - is the stength, the 1 is the reset.

Simple enough? just modify time and strength.

Combine with mpbhops on the block if you want to force bhopping, and if your clever enough integrate it into onehop. Do what you want!
